&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid&#34;&gt;mermaid-js/mermaid: Generation of diagrams like flowcharts or sequence diagrams from text in a similar manner as markdown&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
